<h3 id="note-the-library-cannot-be-built-until-you-finish-the-research-in-the-university">Note: The Library cannot be built until you finish the research in the <a href="../../source/buildings/university">University</a>.</h3>
<p><br /></p>

<p>The Library is a way for you to raise your adult citizensâ€™ Intelligence skill, which influences all other skill increases (at other jobs). A citizen will randomly level up their Intelligence as long as theyâ€™re assigned to the Library. Being a Library Student is their full-time job, so you canâ€™t have one citizen work at the Library and another worker hut at the same time.</p>

<p>Two citizens can study at a time per Library level. So:</p>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Building Level</th>
      <th>Citizens Educated at a Time</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td>1</td>
      <td>2</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>2</td>
      <td>4</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>3</td>
      <td>6</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>4</td>
      <td>8</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>5</td>
      <td>10</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<p><strong>Hint:</strong> Paper helps Library Students increase their skills faster.</p>

<p><br /></p>

